<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>مَا الْقارِعَةُ <span class="c2">(٢)</span><a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَما أَدْراكَ مَا الْقارِعَةُ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>يَوْمَ يَكُونُ النَّاسُ كَالْفَراشِ الْمَبْثُوثِ <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>وَتَكُونُ الْجِبالُ كَالْعِهْنِ الْمَنْفُوشِ <span class="c2">(٥)</span><a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>فَأَمَّا مَنْ ثَقُلَتْ مَوازِينُهُ <span class="c2">(٦)</span><a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>فَهُوَ فِي عِيشَةٍ راضِيَةٍ <span class="c2">(٧)</span><a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>وَأَمَّا مَنْ خَفَّتْ مَوازِينُهُ <span class="c2">(٨)</span><a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>فَأُمُّهُ هاوِيَةٌ <span class="c2">(٩)</span><a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>وَما أَدْراكَ ما هِيَهْ <span class="c2">(١٠)</span><a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>نارٌ حامِيَةٌ <span class="c2">(١١)</span> <span class="c2">«٧»</span><a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
