<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>٤٤- هَلْ أَتاكَ حَدِيثُ الْغاشِيَةِ <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span>وُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ خاشِعَةٌ <span class="c2">(٢)</span><a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
